Frequently Asked Questions

What's the difference between credits and subscriptions?

Credits are one-time purchases for occasional use, while subscriptions give you unlimited access for a recurring fee.

Can I upgrade or downgrade my plan?

Yes! You can change your plan at any time. Credits never expire, and subscriptions can be upgraded immediately.

Do you offer refunds?

We offer a 30-day money-back guarantee on all plans. If you're not satisfied, contact us for a full refund.

Is there a free trial?

Yes! All new users get 10 free trial credits to explore EduPack's features before committing to a plan.
